OL,3,CBoth historic men's interisland
OL,4,Csporting clashes to be held on the
OL,5,Csame day
OL,7,FJersey and Guernsey's biggest
OL,8,Finterisland sporting clashes will be
OL,9,Fheld on the same day this year.
OL,11,FThe Muratti final and the Siam Cup
OL,12,Fbetween Jersey and Guernsey will both
OL,13,Fbe played on May 16th, but in
OL,14,Fdifferent islands.
OL,16,FThe football clash the Muratti will be
OL,17,Fin Jersey and the Siam Cup which is
OL,18,Fthe rugby game will be in Guernsey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
