CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773429075
OL,3,CBoth historic men's interisland
OL,4,Csporting clashes to be held on the
OL,5,Csame day
OL,7,FThe Spring Insure Siam Cup is the
OL,8,Fsecond oldest rugby trophy in the
OL,9,Fworld and is played for by the
OL,10,FGuernsey Raiders and Jersey RFC.
OL,11,FWhilst the Muratti or the Muratti Vase
OL,12,Fis the annual inter-island football
OL,13,Fcompetition between Jersey, Guernsey,
OL,14,Fand Alderney which dates back to 1905.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773429075
OL,3,CBoth historic men's interisland
OL,4,Csporting clashes to be held on the
OL,5,Csame day
OL,7,FTim Pryor, Chief Executive Officer at
OL,8,FJersey FA said: "I don't think it's
OL,9,Fideal that they're on the same day but
OL,10,Fit's two different islands and two
OL,11,Fdifferent audiences in some ways. I
OL,12,Fsuppose it's a shame for some who
OL,13,Fmight want to go to both that there's
OL,14,Fa bit of overlap - I get that. Had the
OL,15,Fgames been in the same island we
OL,16,Fmight've had a bit more thought around
OL,17,Fit."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
