PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773429075
OL,3,CBoth historic men's interisland
OL,4,Csporting clashes to be held on the
OL,5,Csame day
OL,7,FJordan Reynolds, Director of Rugby at
OL,8,FGuernsey Raiders added: "There doesn't
OL,9,Fseem to be an issue about it. Sporting
OL,10,Fevents are always going to be on
OL,11,Fbetween the two islands it just shows
OL,12,Fwe're giving a good selection for
OL,13,Feveryone. People that want to watch
OL,14,Fthe rugby will still come and watch
OL,15,Fthe rugby. I think as a spectacle the
OL,16,FSiam Cup has been massive for a long
OL,17,Ftime."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
