OL,3,CBoth historic men's interisland
OL,4,Csporting clashes to be held on the
OL,5,Csame day
OL,7,FOne game that won't clash though is
OL,8,Fthe women's Muratti. After a few years
OL,9,Fwhere that fixture has been played
OL,10,Fbefore the men's final, it'll instead
OL,11,Fbe played the following weekend on May
OL,12,F23rd, following feedback from the
OL,13,Fplayers.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
